---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Manifiesto de Identidad Digital vs IA | Blog DEVFHM" description="Este no es solo otro manifiesto sobre IA. Es una invitación a dejar de escribir código monótono y empezar a crear ecosistemas digitales vivos a través del diseño humano.">
    
    <Navbar />

    <main class="pt-40 md:pt-48 pb-20">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <header class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-16 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-end">
          <div class="lg:col-span-8 z-10 relative">
            <div
              class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-4 py-1 rounded-full"
            >
              <span
                class="text-[0.7rem] font-black font-headline tracking-widest uppercase"
                >Entrada / 04</span
              >
            </div>
            <h1
              class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter mb-8 text-on-background"
              data-key="article.title"
            >
              Curando el <br />
              <span class="text-primary italic">Futuro</span>
              <span class="text-stroke text-primary">Digital</span>
            </h1>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-8">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-surface-container overflow-hidden"
              >
                <img
                  alt="Author"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  data-alt="close-up portrait of a creative professional man with glasses in a bright modern studio setting"
                  src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC54hd-g-2cFLoU8oHYtk-J2drA_041s0OAOVBb7lYJeKE8VAGay-QyH-WozpqGMqZ5aJrBRNVL3Tq7iUN2sbIEl-H5QnNgX6J7YWzpoGFknb0CqKqb-6uts1U_Zmw5XPA3vncQUE0rT5aXEXMcRclMs9yWTvh_kwDRddKEohdd2kdFH6oiG-KEs790KgKc0FYY9XePhTaUJhfMPcIQ6z9mm5tTZ5GYAT9xnrj4K6uTtaAM_fpAHmKPoIQhzCWOzIaTVUqTxlW48e16"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-headline font-bold text-lg leading-tight">
                  Geek Sloth
                </p>
                <p class="text-outline text-sm">
                  Design Disruptor &amp; Lead Dev
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="h-8 w-[1px] bg-outline-variant/30 mx-2"></div>
              <p class="text-outline text-sm font-medium tracking-wide">
                MARZO 24, 2024 — 8 MIN READ
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="relative w-full aspect-[21/9] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden mt-8 shadow-2xl"
        >
          <img
            alt="Main Hero"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            data-alt="minimalist overhead shot of a clean workspace with a laptop, neon blue lighting accents, and abstract digital interfaces"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAeiTnIv5iIpSjf9fHSzrKLKVczebHLTG_hAz42AuxcXSZlbeKntSgnqNdb-bMuK5jflgM9vzfhRPHxh9QLOt8mnNzYVxQMZx0LCJfxjb5sVPR6QlVwT-TZdG-jZQTKVGFAtkzi_nTVvo2ePEPG6QVnrCF6D4a_f9JxQnLsNIbY_Cp9SonoB_0PAhFCA77wnjBwtXzR_C8tWwR18CZaD9otADVi5PUqR3WZ5zl9ftoXwE_1Nnw4KHZ7v22H26OvNFXSSbOtJ-bQrWDL"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </header>
      <!-- Article Content -->
      <section
        class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16"
      >
        <!-- Side Metadata/Social (Sticky) -->
        <aside class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="sticky top-32 flex flex-col items-center space-y-8">
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline hover:text-primary cursor-pointer transition-colors"
              style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 0"
              >favorite</span
            >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline hover:text-primary cursor-pointer transition-colors"
              >share</span
            >
            <span
              class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline hover:text-primary cursor-pointer transition-colors"
              >bookmark</span
            >
            <div class="h-12 w-[1px] bg-outline-variant/30"></div>
            <span
              class="font-headline font-black text-xs vertical-rl tracking-widest text-outline"
              >SCROLL</span
            >
          </div>
        </aside>
        <!-- Main Reading Area -->
        <article class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-12">
          <div
            class="prose prose-xl prose-slate max-w-none font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed"
          >
            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-on-surface mb-8" data-key="article.intro">
              La intersección entre la estética editorial y la ingeniería de
              software no es solo una tendencia; es el nuevo estándar para
              productos digitales que buscan trascender la saturación visual.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
              <p data-key="article.p1">
                Vivimos en una era donde el usuario ya no solo consume
                información, sino que habita experiencias. El diseño "disruptor"
                no se trata de romper las reglas por el simple hecho de hacerlo,
                sino de entender la arquitectura visual de tal manera que cada
                asimetría tenga un propósito funcional.
              </p>
              <p data-key="article.p2">
                Al eliminar las líneas de cuadrícula tradicionales y apostar por
                espacios negativos masivos, permitimos que el contenido respire.
                Es el silencio en una pieza musical lo que da fuerza a la nota.
                En la UI, el espacio es la nota que sostiene la composición.
              </p>
            </div>
            <h2
              class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6 flex items-center"
              data-key="article.h2"
            >
              <span class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-primary mr-4"></span>
              La Ingeniería del Caos Controlado
            </h2>
            <div
              class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8 mb-12 border-l-4 border-primary"
            >
              <code class="text-primary font-mono text-sm leading-loose" is:raw>
                const disruptDesign = (rules) =&gt; { <br />
                  return rules.map(rule =&gt; ({<br />
                    ...rule,<br />
                    asymmetry: true,<br />
                    whiteSpace: 'massive',<br />
                    impact: 'high-authority'<br />
                  }));<br />
                };
              </code>
            </div>
            <p data-key="article.p3">
              El código anterior ilustra nuestro enfoque. No estamos eliminando
              las reglas, las estamos extendiendo. La "Curaduría Disruptiva"
              requiere un nivel de precisión obsesivo. Cada tipografía Epilogue
              en negrita debe contrastar perfectamente con la legibilidad
              funcional de Manrope.
            </p>
            <!-- Multimedia Block: Video Placeholder -->
            <div
              class="relative aspect-video rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-on-surface/5 group cursor-pointer mb-12"
            >
              <img
                alt="Video Cover"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
                data-alt="futuristic electronic equipment and retro hardware with cyan and magenta ambient lighting in a dark room"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD89kIdY-cdgfeTL9g4SFAY4WjzKy6BO-AgNE7JqiVWVuIjUae4lNnmdbnVbQbj31AZwNqc_HI2pF4gtIvks5ypVfQF4q0xoVV0rBKKPt62xqFxtNjNR7_9lYxkyUG4-J4jL9QTqi0OSxRvmgmV2fnSUMEFyqXk1H9CLFAj7qhaMg1ZG_14Y6n0xUZsgAmQKCnzOEBFcBKDUZct8qCPGnclFbCKwM9ayAj7TEpyfeyJ0pk83xRf-tpVPMHi-0xqrXDPJxI55t-ZOCpS"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div
                  class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                >
                  <span
                    class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl"
                    style="font-variation-settings: &quot;FILL&quot; 1"
                    >play_arrow</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4" data-key="article.h3">
              El Legado de la Estética
            </h3>
            <p data-key="article.p4">
              Finalmente, debemos considerar el impacto emocional. Un diseño que
              se siente "editorial" evoca una sensación de permanencia y
              autoridad. En un mundo de efímeros feeds de redes sociales, el
              contenido curado con una identidad visual fuerte permanece en la
              memoria del usuario mucho después de haber cerrado la pestaña.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Interaction Tags -->
          <div class="pt-12 border-t border-outline-variant/20">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <span
                class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 text-xs font-headline font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer"
                >DESIGN SYSTEM</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 text-xs font-headline font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer"
                >ARCHITECTURE</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 text-xs font-headline font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer"
                >MINIMALISM</span
              >
              <span
                class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 text-xs font-headline font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer"
                >DEVELOPMENT</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- Sidebar Info / Newsletter -->
        <aside class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-12">
          <!-- Card removed -->
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <h4
              class="font-headline font-bold text-lg border-l-4 border-secondary px-4"
            >
              Tendencias
            </h4>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="group cursor-pointer">
                <span class="text-xs font-black text-primary/50 block mb-1"
                  >01 / CONCEPT</span
                >
                <h5
                  class="font-headline font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                >
                  Micro-interacciones en VR: El futuro del tacto visual
                </h5>
              </div>
              <div class="group cursor-pointer">
                <span class="text-xs font-black text-primary/50 block mb-1"
                  >02 / DEV</span
                >
                <h5
                  class="font-headline font-bold leading-tight group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                >
                  Por qué Tailwind CSS es el fin de las hojas de estilo gigantes
                </h5>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>
      <!-- Related Articles Grid -->
      <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mt-32">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-12">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter" data-key="article.related_title">
              Artículos Relacionados
            </h2>
            <p class="text-outline mt-2">
              Continúa explorando el ecosistema disruptor.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-2 text-primary font-bold hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform"
            href="/blog"
          >
            <span data-key="article.view_all">Ver todos</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_40px_60px_rgba(26,28,28,0.04)] group"
          >
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden relative">
              <img
                alt="Related 1"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                data-alt="abstract digital artwork showing floating geometric cubes with high contrast lighting and shadows"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBKxqeD2Fb9JN_54CZniv5vKcQ1BFbjZX76K19FQJ1XacshPN7Gf8LQ7dpOlh1D_3huKqMxZ659rTW0Wtxi7YsTaauhlmTlJP6_u2zWe7-t6_B4rZxZtorTOejwPGPVtKN1Y9T9fZikXtJUr825civP-sIICy9gf9zwLYTf2FcS6AbUfdD63P0fRu7uwA5uEjfip5Kkd4NKUSNWacZg497ixBSwCUq7KIxgfjJ6k37hUs9DpwyIGkLWalAHjjZvhRTL0R6-Ul0PTFvc"
              />
              <span
                class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black font-headline tracking-widest text-primary"
                >IDENTITY</span
              >
              <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 pointer-events-none"
              >
                <span class="font-headline font-black text-6xl">01</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3
                class="font-headline font-bold text-xl leading-snug mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors line-clamp-2"
              >
                Navegación Fantasma: Cómo guiar al usuario sin menús
              </h3>
              <div
                class="flex items-center text-outline text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest"
              >
                <span>Geek Sloth</span>
                <span class="mx-2">•</span>
                <span>5 MIN READ</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_40px_60px_rgba(26,28,28,0.04)] group"
          >
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden relative">
              <img
                alt="Related 2"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                data-alt="close-up of clean lines of modern architecture with deep shadows and vibrant blue sky background"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC-16va9GkViL0EZEcHskfDiNnhLUuaScco_ERrN5xkmfFi-x53RKD-J-rC5ZbmQ2hz85oB48eupl01LY8UlOTdq6kKFUG_eJyEBUYXs0hPVlex16W8PEYo7gd5yb1PuZfwEBCMsjyiElHOObZF2KCM0bQns9vT0ORaYMblVK52lgbaRgU8ULHVXAoXKdUqhCuNPV5qWG5yJRqYKUytcjqlrb90VHWXBH1ZscwOqLhbSH5KBmQBgCksYttnrRFuz30KIDQINVfsCIHt"
              />
              <span
                class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black font-headline tracking-widest text-primary"
                >STRATEGY</span
              >
              <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 pointer-events-none"
              >
                <span class="font-headline font-black text-6xl">02</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3
                class="font-headline font-bold text-xl leading-snug mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors line-clamp-2"
              >
                Asimetría Intencional: El fin de las rejillas de 12 columnas
              </h3>
              <div
                class="flex items-center text-outline text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest"
              >
                <span>Geek Sloth</span>
                <span class="mx-2">•</span>
                <span>12 MIN READ</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_40px_60px_rgba(26,28,28,0.04)] group"
          >
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden relative">
              <img
                alt="Related 3"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                data-alt="minimalist 3D render of soft flowing organic shapes in shades of white and light blue"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAa_hbwYc7Wo4Vh729fkXwq9rTKOEn1mxwEHi-Fg5fH4guQb99Hqn9BqJuFlSMMBy9u9mrYjrLwb2mnGknq7d4Wr6IoIpRiU0LgA1Jd0TJIb_GiftvpBfQRhwAnzE-ddcUTtAIbPTShapuaJAFp4C5MfAg14DbF444Htes3KPxHOHkRmJQqodTDq0Yk22ir20TLzMYdfbcl_H13OdNrn4rWbsQR9PTiIAnWvjO85YlXWX6CS-gqQivfpiyzTcK3QgGq6qU2OKnRt2d6"
              />
              <span
                class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black font-headline tracking-widest text-primary"
                >UI/UX</span
              >
              <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 pointer-events-none"
              >
                <span class="font-headline font-black text-6xl">03</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3
                class="font-headline font-bold text-xl leading-snug mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors line-clamp-2"
              >
                Psicología del Color Neón en Entornos Profesionales
              </h3>
              <div
                class="flex items-center text-outline text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest"
              >
                <span>Geek Sloth</span>
                <span class="mx-2">•</span>
                <span>7 MIN READ</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="px-8">
        <div class="premium-value-strip">
          <div>
            <strong>Insight Aplicable</strong>
            <p>Cada entrada prioriza ideas que puedes ejecutar en producto hoy.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Calidad Editorial</strong>
            <p>Narrativa técnica diseñada para equipos de diseño y desarrollo.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Lectura Accesible</strong>
            <p>Tipografía, contraste y ritmo de contenido optimizados para lectura.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
    <script is:inline>
      // Sidebar Parallax
      document.addEventListener("mousemove", (e) => {
        const mouseX = (e.clientX / window.innerWidth - 0.5) * 10;
        const mouseY = (e.clientY / window.innerHeight - 0.5) * 10;

        gsap.to("aside", {
          x: mouseX,
          y: mouseY,
          duration: 1.5,
          ease: "power2.out",
        });
      });
    </script>
    
  
</Layout>
